<h1 class="page-title">About Timerrapp</h1>

<p class="page-subtitle">Timerrapp is a free collection of online clocks and timers — no ads,
no account, no download required. It works in any browser on any device.</p>

<p style="color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--font-body);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1rem;">Tools available: clock, alarm, timer, stopwatch, Pomodoro, world clock,
ADHD timer, chess clock, and binary clock.</p>

<p style="color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--font-body);line-height:1.7;">Built for anyone who needs a fast, clean, distraction-free time tool.</p>